goals__remit: The Onassis Foundation’s activities are multifarious, focused on very important areas such as culture, education, environment, health and social solidarity.
relevant_communication: Within the framework of its public benefit activity, the Onassis Foundation responded to the need for the urban revival of Athens by funding and organizing the Architectural Competition and all the Architectural, Bioclimatic and Technical Studies relative to the Rethink Athens project (www.rethinkathens.org).
